casebody.head_matter:
Albania DELEON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 12-9748.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 7, 2013.
Case below, 704 F.3d 189.
Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Order entered June 3, 2013, vacated. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.
